            <title>[JDK-8321972] test runtime/Unsafe/InternalErrorTest.java timeout on linux-riscv64 platform</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8321972</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>This issue happens after &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8320886&quot; title=&quot;Unsafe_SetMemory0 is not guarded&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8320886&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8320886&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Unsafe_SetMemory0 is not guarded which added testing Unsafe.setMemory, trying to access next page after truncation.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
The test pass if changing NUM_TESTS to 3, like:&lt;br/&gt;
